2v5", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ip7x12v5", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "宠辱皆忘", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/adf8/26b7/277700_mini.png?m=1730873239", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/adf8/26b7/277700_normal.png?m=1730873239", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/adf8/26b7/277700_large.png?m=1730873239", "created": 1514519191, "last_modified": 1730873239, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ip7x12v5", "last_touched": 1754656647, "title": "公司估计要倒了，如何自救？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1151844", "created": 1754982423, "deleted": 0, "content": "各种小道消息公司没钱了，果然这个月工资延期发放，没有任何公告和通知。\r\n现在每月还有 1 万的房贷，压力甚大，也没啥积蓄，如何才能保住现有的房子。\r\n是不是可以像银行申请延期还款？没有过类似经验", "content_rendered": "<p>各种小道消息公司没钱了，果然这个月工资延期发放，没有任何公告和通知。\n现在每月还有 1 万的房贷，压力甚大，也没啥积蓄，如何才能保住现有的房子。\n是不是可以像银行申请延期还款？没有过类似经验</p>\n", "last_modified": 1754982423, "replies": 66, "id": 1151844}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1695370146", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1695370146", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 20872, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146", "stars": 3490, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"id": 118668, "username": "shuijinliuxi", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/shuijinliuxi", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6d221783a7a4a89f8512565c4e7b60e3?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6d221783a7a4a89f8512565c4e7b60e3?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6d221783a7a4a89f8512565c4e7b60e3?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1432527893, "last_modified": 1432527893, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "since640", "last_touched": 1755056170, "title": "目前在广州，面到一个日本那边的国内公司，过了终面，想请教大佬们一些问题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1151917", "created": 1755002058, "deleted": 0, "content": "目前在广州，工作主要做的是前端，上家公司裁员了，薪资 22K ，年底 1~3 个月；\r\n\r\n这个月先找了一个公司先干着，薪资 18K ，年底 0~2 个月。\r\n\r\n因为对目前的薪资不满意，所以还一直在面试，\r\n\r\n目前面到了一个在日本那边的国内公司，bc game: https://bc.game/ ，主要做博彩和区块链的，目前已经过了终面，在薪资这块需要我给对方，但我不知道怎么给，有没有大佬能给点建议，房子公司有 1000 刀的补贴，还有 500 刀的吃的补贴，公司也提供两餐。\r\n\r\n以及这公司靠不靠谱，在日本那边怎样（虽然对方说拿到合规经营）", "content_rendered": "<p>目前在广州，工作主要做的是前端，上家公司裁员了，薪资 22K ，年底 1~3 个月；</p>\n<p>这个月先找了一个公司先干着，薪资 18K ，年底 0~2 个月。</p>\n<p>因为对目前的薪资不满意，所以还一直在面试，</p>\n<p>目前面到了一个在日本那边的国内公司，bc game: <a href=\"https://bc.game/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://bc.game/</a> ，主要做博彩和区块链的，目前已经过了终面，在薪资这块需要我给对方，但我不知道怎么给，有没有大佬能给点建议，房子公司有 1000 刀的补贴，还有 500 刀的吃的补贴，公司也提供两餐。</p>\n<p>以及这公司靠不靠谱，在日本那边怎样（虽然对方说拿到合规经营）</p>\n", "last_modified": 1755002480, "replies": 64, "id": 1151917}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 67767, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9389, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 430324, "username": "skyrim61", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/skyrim61", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0efb/92d8/430324_mini.png?m=1734571590", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0efb/92d8/430324_normal.png?m=1734571590", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0efb/92d8/430324_large